        '3' => 'In some cases, we may also share your data with analytical or marketing partners when necessary to improve our services or offer personalized features. This information is generally anonymized or aggregated to prevent direct identification. When such sharing involves personal data, it is conducted only after obtaining your explicit consent, in compliance with our legal obligations.',
