        '1' => 'The security of your personal data is at the heart of our concerns. We recognize the importance of protecting the information you share with us and have implemented strict technical, organizational, and procedural measures to ensure its confidentiality, integrity, and availability. These measures aim to prevent unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction of the data we collect and process. We commit to maintaining these security standards and adapting them continually in response to evolving technologies and potential threats.',
        '2' => 'Our systems are protected by state-of-the-art technologies, such as encryption of sensitive data, firewalls, and intrusion detection mechanisms. Connections to the site are secured using HTTPS protocols, ensuring that the information exchanged between your device and our servers remains confidential and cannot be intercepted. Additionally, user passwords are stored in encrypted form, making their recovery or unauthorized use impossible, even in the event of unauthorized access to our databases.',
        '3' => 'Internally, only authorized members of our staff or partners with a legitimate need for access in the context of their duties can view your personal data. These individuals are bound by strict confidentiality obligations and must follow rigorous procedures when handling information. Any violation of internal rules is subject to appropriate sanctions under our internal policies and applicable laws.',
        '4' => 'We regularly conduct security audits and penetration tests to identify and correct any potential vulnerabilities in our infrastructure. These audits are carried out by independent cybersecurity experts to ensure objective and thorough assessments. The results of these evaluations are used to improve our systems and strengthen our defenses against emerging threats. Additionally, we maintain incident response procedures to react quickly and effectively in the event of a security issue, minimizing potential impacts on your data.',
        '5' => 'While we do everything possible to protect your data, it is important to remember that no security system is infallible. Users also play a key role in securing their personal information. We strongly recommend choosing strong, unique passwords for your account, not sharing your credentials with third parties, and monitoring your account for any suspicious activity. If you believe your account security has been compromised, please inform us immediately so that we can take the necessary measures.',
        '6' => 'We also work with partners and subcontractors who adhere to strict security standards aligned with our requirements. All data transfers to these third parties are conducted securely, and we regularly verify their compliance with commitments related to personal data protection. Our contracts with these third parties include specific clauses guaranteeing the confidentiality and security of shared information.',
        '7' => 'In the event of a confirmed data security breach that poses a high risk to your rights or freedoms, we commit to informing you as soon as possible, in accordance with our legal obligations. We will also collaborate with the relevant authorities to resolve the situation transparently and promptly. Our goal is to minimize any potential impact on your personal data and restore our systems security as quickly as possible.',
