    'cookies' => [
        'title' => '8. Cookies and Similar Technologies',
        '1' => 'When you browse our site, we use cookies and other similar technologies to enhance your user experience, personalize content, and collect data necessary for analyzing the use of our platform. These technologies are essential to the proper functioning of our services and help optimize the features provided while meeting your expectations.',
        '2' => 'Cookies are small text files stored on your device (computer, smartphone, or tablet) when you visit our site. They contain information that allows us to recognize your device during subsequent visits and tailor our services to your preferences. These cookies can be temporary, expiring when you close your browser, or persistent, remaining on your device for a specified duration.',
        '3' => 'We use different types of cookies, including essential cookies, performance cookies, customization cookies, and analytics cookies. Essential cookies are crucial for accessing basic features, such as logging into your account or securely navigating the platform. Performance cookies help us measure the effectiveness of our services and identify potential improvements. Customization cookies allow content and features to be tailored to your preferences, while analytics cookies collect data on overall platform usage to optimize its design and usability.',
